title: 11/19/2020 - Best of The Herd
itunes:title: 11/19/2020 - Best of The Herd
description:
-We don't know who any of the NBA prospects are and it's hurting the league

-The Seahawks beating the Cardinals is a lock because Kyler has pressure on him

-LaMelo Ball will not be a star in the NBA

-The Warriors dynasty feels over

-Philadelphia is still celebrating their Super Bowl win and now they are unraveling


Guest: Greg Cosell, NFL Films
